{"tid":2286630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"另立民間議會","createTime":"2020-11-15T07:05:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T05:30:39.000Z","uid":89937,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"22e9356d84007bff0f33666cceed7cae33031428","tid":2286630,"uid":89937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T07:05:54.000Z","msg":"忽然覺得民主派應該另立民間議會，邀請埋DQ6（唔計去咗紐西蘭嘅姚松炎）+范國威+區諾軒+再邀請埋初選勝出者<br />\n<br />\n就算姿態都好，起碼Discredit咗而家個橡皮圖章議會先，有個大少少組織嘅名銜，之後去外國戰線都容易啲，<br />\n<br />\n同埋亦可以避免民主黨一個話晒事（而家好多外國傳媒都仲係搵民主黨）"},{"pid":"bbe70b4b032c257d59746e99fb66483b56fd3bb8","tid":2286630,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T07:07:00.000Z","msg":"1. 議題<br />\n2. 點樣先可以有效率咁發表意見"},{"pid":"048cd2adc61b7790bda765ad2b3de1bfcd10d900","tid":2286630,"uid":89937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bbe70b4b032c257d59746e99fb66483b56fd3bb8","tid":2286630,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T07:07:00.000Z","msg":"1. 議題<br />\n2. 點樣先可以有效率咁發表意見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T07:10:26.000Z","msg":"議題：我諗都係『香港危機』為主，點樣贏呢場仗，但如果仲有一啲民生議題處理，暫時都可以借一啲（原）雙料議員名義去做。"},{"pid":"c0ccba0fa5ca756a24541a94ad2e0fb75d758a88","tid":2286630,"uid":89937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T22:38:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"73ecab6a2a3aaafbabb9cc6fcc3b8eac16fafa1f","tid":2286630,"uid":124134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T22:51:31.000Z","msg":"舊年區選已經講過啦   無人做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5439e23d940c5e7105737c3cb015383119d8a822","tid":2286630,"uid":362900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T22:59:49.000Z","msg":"$ ?"},{"pid":"48fedee50648803b5b203ea07b0cc922c7d3d97c","tid":2286630,"uid":89937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"73ecab6a2a3aaafbabb9cc6fcc3b8eac16fafa1f","tid":2286630,"uid